reviewText: Even though it doesnt matter cause this dvd is not real new but it was just ok. It does have very beautiful models but the camera work is sub-par for example, when shooting video of bikini girls i don't want to see the other photographers just focus on the model. Also when u call the dvd bikini allstars maybe less interview time like alot less, unneeded, but the girls are very pretty and the bikinis are pretty small. Too much extra intros and outros form one segment to an other and use the whole dvd u know they have the footage to fill it up. pretty good dvd
